        <mxCell id="legend-text" value="Field-Based: Users select which fields to include (17 available) | Fire-and-Forget: Never blocks test execution | Multi-Webhook: Supports multiple active webhooks | Template Support: Google Chat cards, Slack blocks, generic JSON | Timeout: 5 seconds per webhook | Error Handling: Silent failure, log only&#xa;Colors: Green=Triggers/External | Purple=Service | Orange=Payload | Cyan=HTTP | Red Cylinders=DB" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=6.5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
